
======================================================================
CRED-001 SSH key access [CRITICAL]
======================================================================

Category:
  Credential Theft  (detector: rules)

Description:
  Accessing SSH private keys during build/install

Recommendation:
  Package should never access user SSH keys

CWE: CWE-522

Related Codes:
  CRED-002, CRED-003, BROWSER-001, BROWSER-002

